    <div id="proposal">
        Roshika, my love, you are the dawn that breaks my darkness, the melody that dances through my soul. Every heartbeat whispers your name, every dream paints your smile. I‚Äôve searched the stars and found my universe in you. Will you let me love you, cherish you, and hold you close for all eternity? Be mine, my forever muse.
